@@ -0,0 +1,20 @@
+package bookstore
+
+import (
+	"errors"
+)
+
+// Book represents information about a book.
+type Book struct {
+	Title  string
+	Author string
+	Copies int
+}
+
+func Buy(b Book) (Book, error) {
+	if b.Copies < 1 {
+		return Book{}, errors.New("not enough copy")
+	}
+	b.Copies--
+	return b, nil
+}
